author: Amanda Prestigiacomo
description: GE Appliances announced this week that it’s moving even more of its production from China to GOP-led state Kentucky, and investing nearly half-a-billion dollars. title: GE Appliances Moving Production From China To Republican State

description: Two people were killed and at least 14 wounded when a Russian drone smashed into a residential high-rise in Ukraine’s Black Sea city of Odesa, authorities said on Saturday. Three children were among the wounded in the overnight attack, with one in critical condition, said regional Governor Oleh Kiper. Footage posted by the State Emergency ...
title: Russian Drone Strike Kills 2, Wounds 14 In Ukraine’s Odesa, Authorities Say
